	1.9.2

2010-09-02  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	Context: set_dash(): Make the dashes parameter const.

	* cairomm/context.[h|cc]: set_dash(): Add versions that take a const
	vector parameter, deprecating the old versions.

