2006-07-05  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

2006-07-05  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	* cairomm/context.h:
	* cairomm/fontface.h:
	* cairomm/pattern.h:
	* cairomm/surface.cc:
